name: 40/20's into FTP #1
description:
40/20's are an effective workout on their own. Complement these by finishing with a 10-minute Threshold effort, and you are in for a big session! The opening 40/20's target your VO2max system, but the accumulated lactate will influence the fuel source for the culminating Threshold effort.
